%Lee starts out the battle with an attack.
%The timing is tight, and failure to guard will 
%freeze Mario for one turn.
%Removed copying partners because I honestly
%don't feel like editing each of those.

@	$Lee
{
	[MaxHP]        55`b
	[PowerBounce]  30`b
}

#new:IdleAnimations $IdleAnimations_LeeDead
{
	.Status:Normal    00A4000C
	.Status:End
}


